title: [SOLVED] 820-3330 No TP/KB
message:
Hey! 
Got this board with mild damage by SMC. Also C4920, R5313 and C5304 were knocked off but have been replaced. Everything seems to work but TP and KB. 

R5806 - 18.7 V
Pin 22 of J5800 - 3.3V

Here are diode measurements of J5800

2 - 0

4 - .683

8 - .683
9 - .656
10 - .683
11 - .685

13 - .686
14 - .964
15 - .688
16 - .686
17 - .561
18 - O.L
19 - .656
20 - .696
21 - .582
22 - .368

Pn 49 & 22 of U5701 have 3.3V

USB KB and Mouse both work. Multiple TP's and cables tested.

title: [SOLVED] 820-3330 No TP/KB
message: Check all traces from U5701 to the trackpad. Also check the 18V supply to trackpad, it needs to be connected to check this.

title: [SOLVED] 820-3330 No TP/KB
message:
R7803 was good. All traces were good. Noticed that BT was also missing in sys report which I should have notice much earlier.  Replaced U2700. All is good. Thanks again for the assistance GB and as always Duke.
Have a good one guys.
